title.narrative: Ebola Crisis Unit - Front Line Delivery

description.narrative: This activity (Ebola Crisis Unit - Front Line Delivery) is a component of Ebola Crisis Unit - Front Line Delivery reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Front Line Delivery' and a budget of £5,631,034. The start date is 10-10-2014 and the end date is 31-03-2021.
